Output assets/vhs/readme-prompt.gif

Set FontSize 46
Set FontFamily "UDEV Gothic NF"
Set Width 1220
Set Height 530
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 48
Set BorderRadius 10
Set Framerate 24
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "assets/vhs/run-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 800ms
Show
Sleep 500ms
Type "cd capsule"
Enter
Sleep 3000ms

Screenshot assets/vhs/readme-prompt.png
Sleep 2s
